<li>
<p>Menu (gear button) pressed</p></li>
<li>
<p>SCHome RC Button</p></li>
<li>
<p>Partner Button</p></li>
<li>
<p>WF+ Button</p></li>
<li>
<p>Input Button</p></li>
<li>
<p>MIC Button</p></li>
<li>
<p>Any action that dismisses the side menu (currently)</p></li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>As a user, I would like to dismiss the quick settings menu when I press:=
</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Actions highlighted left</p></li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd">3</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><span data-colorid=3D"q5i7ocgmx9">Game Bar displays instead of Quick men=
